    "---\n",
    "## 1. Standard Project Folders\n",
    "\n",
    "### Core folders used in this project\n",
    "- `data/raw`: original source files (never edited directly).\n",
    "- `data/processed`: cleaned or transformed data.\n",
    "- `notebooks`: exploratory and milestone notebooks.\n",
    "- `scripts`: reusable Python scripts.\n",
    "- `outputs`: generated artifacts such as reports or exported files.\n",
    "\n",
    "This separation avoids path confusion and accidental overwrites."
