    "---\n",
    "## 3. Separating Code, Data, and Outputs\n",
    "\n",
    "Use this workflow to prevent organizational mistakes:\n",
    "1. Keep original files in `data/raw`.\n",
    "2. Save cleaned data in `data/processed`.\n",
    "3. Keep notebook logic in `notebooks` and reusable logic in `scripts`.\n",
    "4. Store generated artifacts in `outputs`.\n",
    "\n",
    "Never overwrite raw input files during experimentation."
